description	"Archetype: Rebel Vanguard

Class: Arc Trooper.
Class Summary:
A multi-life soldier with a single-use rocket, variety of grenades and an evasive roll. 

Weaponry:
- Pistol (2)
- DH-17 (3)
- MiniMag PTL Rocket Launcher (1)
- Frag Grenade (1)
- Sonic Detonator (1)
- Concussion Grenade (1)

Attributes:
- Reinforcements (2)
- Dodge (2) (Activates simultaneously with Sprint)
- Assemble

Abilities:
- Stamina (2) [Class Special 1]
- Dexterity (1) [Class Special 2]

The men and women of the Rebel Alliance were fiercely dedicated to the principle of freedom, and would lay down their lives to win their objectives. Rebel Vanguards were specialized in using heavy weaponry on the battlefield."